from performing arts materials

00:03:40.820 --> 00:03:43.380
through spoken word,
industry recordings,

00:03:43.380 --> 00:03:45.320
all phases of recorded sound.

00:03:45.320 --> 00:03:49.330
So, it's, sort of, a
completist archive in that sense.

00:03:49.330 --> 00:03:51.770
